summary:
**Capital Raising Announcement:**  
- **Structure:** Placement + attaching options  
- **Total raised:** AUD $396,000 (before costs)  
- **Key details:**  
  - Placement price: $0.012/share  
  - Terms: 1 free option per 2 New Shares (exercise price $0.024, 3-year expiry)  
  - Settlement date: 18 July 2025  
  - Options subject to shareholder approval (to be sought September 2025)  
  - Lead manager fees: 6% of funds raised + 3.5M options (subject to approval)  

**Exploration Update (material for valuation):**  
- Drilling to commence at Phoenix Copper Project, targeting:  
  - Trenton Prospect (~1.8km strike, avg. 2.79% Cu)  
  - Philadelphia Prospect (750m strike, avg. 6.29% Cu, 219 g/t Ag)
